Description: # Feishu Bot
        ## Install
        ```
        pip install feishu_bot
        ```
        ## Getting Started
        ```
        from feishu_bot import FeishuBot
        
        bot = FeishuBot('your_app_id', 'your_app_secret')
        await bot.send_text('test')
        ```
        ## Features
        - Automatically token management
        - Cache embeded
